	Enemies

Crawler
	Upper half of an infected human, crawls somewhat aimlessly and may target you
Runner
	Running zombie, accelerates toward you
Zomboid
	Flocking zombies that like to stay in groups
Wallhugger
	Follows your position along the wall, to strike when you go for a door or wall
Spectre
	Somewhat invisible ghost that (maybe) uses displacement map instead of texture. Maybe immune to bullets
Banshee
	Darkens the room with its shrieks


	Items

Torch
	Place at your position to illuminate an area for some time


	Weapons

Pistol
	It's a pistol